org.mpxj.reader

Interface ProjectReader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractProjectFileReader, AbstractProjectReader, AbstractProjectStreamReader, AstaFileReader, AstaJdbcReader, AstaMdbReader, AstaSqliteReader, AstaTextFileReader, ConceptDrawProjectReader, EdrawProjectReader, FastTrackReader, GanttDesignerReader, GanttProjectReader, MerlinReader, MPDDatabaseReader, MPDFileReader, MPPReader, MPXReader, MSPDIReader, OpenPlanReader, P3DatabaseReader, P3PRXFileReader, PhoenixReader, PlannerReader, PrimaveraDatabaseFileReader, PrimaveraDatabaseReader, PrimaveraPMFileReader, PrimaveraXERFileReader, ProjectCommanderReader, ProjectLibreReader, SageReader, SDEFReader, SureTrakDatabaseReader, SureTrakSTXFileReader, SynchroReader, TurboProjectReader, UniversalProjectReader

    public interface ProjectReader
    This interface is implemented by all classes which can read project files of any type and generate an ProjectFile instance from the contents of the file.
